---
// Benefits Section - Business Value Proposition
---

<section
    id="benefits"
    class="bg-white relative overflow-hidden"
    style="padding-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 100px;"
>
    <!-- Background Decor -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-100 to-transparent opacity-50"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col items-center">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-24 max-w-3xl">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide mb-6"
            >
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></span>
                <span>MEASURABLE OUTCOMES</span>
            </div>

            <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-950 mb-6 tracking-tight"
                style="margin-top: 20px;"
            >
                Transform Your <span class="text-teal-600">Bottom Line</span>
            </h2>

            <p
                class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"
                style="margin-top: 20px;"
            >
                Move beyond simple tracking. Our platform delivers measurable
                business outcomes that help you lead the LPG distribution
                market.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefits Grid -->
        <div
            class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto"
            style="margin-top: 20px;"
        >
            <!-- Outcome 1 -->
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-900/5 h-full flex flex-col"
                style="padding: 15px;"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            d="M13 17h8m0 0V9m0 8l-8-8-4 4-6-6"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-[22px] font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors tracking-tight"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Cut Asset Losses by 40%
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[15px]"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Eliminate cylinder vanishing acts with end-to-end GPS and
                    IoT tracking. Every asset accounted for, every time.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-auto px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50/50 rounded-full text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold border border-blue-100 uppercase tracking-wider text-center"
                    style="margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Asset Protection
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Outcome 2 -->
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-900/5 h-full flex flex-col"
                style="padding: 15px;"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-[22px] font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors tracking-tight"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Boost Delivery Speed by 3x
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[15px]"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Automated route optimization and digital dispatching
                    eliminate manual bottlenecks and idling time.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-auto px-4 py-2 bg-teal-50/50 rounded-full text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold border border-teal-100 uppercase tracking-wider text-center"
                    style="margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Logistics Speed
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Outcome 3 -->
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-900/5 h-full flex flex-col"
                style="padding: 15px;"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-[22px] font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors tracking-tight"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Zero-Error Compliance
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[15px]"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Digital safety records and automated auditing ensure 100%
                    regulatory compliance without the paperwork headache.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-auto px-4 py-2 bg-purple-50/50 rounded-full text-purple-700 text-xs font-bold border border-purple-100 uppercase tracking-wider text-center"
                    style="margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Regulatory Safety
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Outcome 4 -->
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-900/5 h-full flex flex-col"
                style="padding: 15px;"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-[22px] font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors tracking-tight"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    24/7 Fleet Visibility
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[15px]"
                    style="margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Know exactly where every cylinder is, from production line
                    to customer doorstep, in real-time.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-auto px-4 py-2 bg-orange-50/50 rounded-full text-orange-700 text-xs font-bold border border-orange-100 uppercase tracking-wider text-center"
                    style="margin-top: 7px;"
                >
                    Real-time Insight
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ROI Calculator CTA -->
        <div
            class="mx-auto bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-10 lg:p-16 shadow-2xl text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden"
            style="margin-top: 20px;
                   max-width: 1280px;"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-teal-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-32 -mb-32"
            >
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 relative z-10">
                Ready to See Your <span class="text-teal-400"
                    >Potential ROI?</span
                >
            </h3>
            <p
                class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10"
            >
                Calculate how much you could save with AgeniumTrack. Most
                clients see full ROI within 6 months of implementation.
            </p>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center relative z-10"
            >
                <a
                    href="#contact"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-500 text-white font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/20"
                >
                    <span>Request ROI Analysis</span>
                    <svg
                        class="w-5 h-5"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a
                    href="#contact"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full border border-white/10 transition-all"
                >
                    <span>Talk to an Expert</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
